NextJS:

Next.js is a React framework that enables server-side rendering (SSR), static site generation (SSG), 
API routes, and many other advanced features. It is built on top of React and enhances it by providing better performance, 
SEO benefits, and a structured development experience.

Key features:
1.SSR : Pages can be pre-rendered on server & sent to the client , improving performance and SEO. 

2. SSG: Nextjs can generate static pages at build time, making them super fast. 

3.Hybrid Rendering: You can choose SSR or SSG on a per-page basis, offering flexibility.

4.Built-in Image Optimization: Next.js provides automatic image optimization using the <Image> component.

5. Automatic Code Splitting: Loads only the required JavaScript for each page, improving performance.
